Description: 

Continuation of the famous strategy of "Behind Enemy Lines 2: Storm" offers 
a new single player mode, in which you will take part in a variety of military operations - from the grand tank battles to covert sniper sabotage.

In multiplayer, you will be able to compete against rivals in the new 
multiplayer maps formats from "1 to 1" to "4 by 4". A new command mode for 16 participants ("8 by 8") would test their skills in large-scale and spectacular battles on huge, detailed maps. 

Also available new types of camouflage, which vary depending 
on the time of year and the type of terrain on the battlefield.

"Behind Enemy Lines: Storm 2" also contains many improvements and changes designed 
to improve the quality of the game in all aspects.
